title: John Zorn-Yamataka Eye - Nani Nani (FLAC)
description:
Nani Nani is an album of improvised music by American composer and saxophonist/multi-instrumentalist John Zorn (as Dekoboko Hajime) and Yamataka Eye.


Track listing

"Eep Man" - 1:07 
"Test Tube" - 3:11 
"Thank You For Not Thinking" - 2:36 
"Pulp Wars" - 2:57 
"Sticky Beethoven's Pipeline" - 1:15 
"Laughing Eskimo" - 1:28 
"Damascus" - 1:11 
"Yoga Dollar" - 5:17 
"Propolution" - 1:36 
"My Rainbow Life" - 1:44 
"Bad Hawkwind" - 18:13 
All compositions by John Zorn/Yamataka Eye 


Yamataka Eye: Vocal, Drums, Toys 
John Zorn: Sax, Harmonica, Guitar, Sitar, Sampler
